{"id":201098,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":10,"day":24}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"人民科学","column":"","genre":"","count":"563","ytitle":"","mtitle":"说说肥料三要素(鼓词)","ftitle":"","authors":["新地"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼好，产量高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说来肥料顶重要；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料好比大米饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植物吃了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能长得好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料种类多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其中包括三要素:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一是氮、二是燐、三是钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们对于植物生长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最有功效!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一说氮素的功效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田地里，用了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼长得咶咶叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶子多，秆儿高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长快速，颜色好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是切切要注意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用它过多大不妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不但枝叶生长太繁茂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且妨碍开花结果了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且收获反不早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾壳往往会压倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么损失就不小!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"氮案肥料非常多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最出名的就是人粪尿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基余家禽家畜粪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廊肥、沙和酒糟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有绿肥和堆肥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动物血粉和油饼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及那化学肥科硫酸铔(即氮素肥田粉)。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石灰氮氮、智利硝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二说燐素的功效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子发芽顶需要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"育了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼根长得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植物易熟收成早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子生成不可少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说到它的种类多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨灰、骨粉、麦糠和鸟粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及那化学肥料:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过燐酸石灰、汤马斯燐肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使用起来都很好!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三说钾素的功效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茎叶生长最主要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了抗病又抗虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还可以构成淀粉、蛋白质，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果实芬芳彩色好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茎杆软弱易折断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且淀粉、糖分少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品质不良果实小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若说它有那几种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草木灰最合用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其次化学肥料氯化钾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硫酸钾镁、碳酸钾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样施用都生效。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以上说完三要素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料常识已知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年收成好不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料使用有多少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大生产，在服梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动勤“上集赢了!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)一般人多数施肥为“上粪”。"}]}